{% comment %}
  Warning's section.
    Designed for you to display various error types, some examples below;
  
  - No Javascript
  - No Cookies (GDPR)
  - Old Browser
{% endcomment %}
<noscript>
  <div class="c-warning is-medium is-visible">
    <span class="c-warning__title">Warning</span>
    <p class="c-warning__body">
      Your browser does not support JavaScript, or it has been disabled.
      {{ shop.name }} may not work properly without JavaScript enabled.
      <a href="https://www.enable-javascript.com/" target="_blank">
        Follow these instructions
      </a>
      to enable JavaScript in your web browser.
    </p>
  </div>
</noscript>